  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201305/ca59b3e726274f518deae8f099b9af1a.jpg\" style=\"border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-left: 0px; margin-right: 5px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t《英文天天写》是沪江部落一档写作类节目，其目的在于提升大家的英语写作能力。每期节目主持人都会给出一个话题，积极参加的童鞋还会得到主持人的专业点评哦！想提高英语写作的童鞋千万不要错过哦！<a href=\"http://pass.hujiang.com/signup/?source=en_sqyd&amp;url=http://st.hujiang.com/131781224/c2561/order2/\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0,90,148);\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201304/d5e293c817a6488d819f0c13a95230e1.jpg\" style=\"border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-left: 0px; line-height: 1.8em; margin-right: 5px;\" /></a>去沪江部落订阅本节目！</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>话题：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tWriting: imagine a scenario or express your opinion<br />\n\tTowel<br />\n\tTowel is very useful in absorbing <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/liquid\" target=\"_blank\">liquid</a>. Who is using the towel? Why is the person using it? What does the towel look like?<br />\n\tThis week's topic: They took the towels from the <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/rack\" target=\"_blank\">rack</a>... (90-110 words)</p>\n<p>\n\tSuggestions:<br />\n\t1) during a tennis practice<br />\n\t2) after getting out from the swimming pool<br />\n\t3) asking room service for towels at a hotel<br />\n\t4) buying towels from the department store<br />\n\t5) Instead of writing a scenario, feel free to comment on the story below.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tIn the quiet locker room, a figure approached a locker. Inside the locker, there was a <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/bulky\" target=\"_blank\">bulky</a> bag. He opened the bag and found what he was looking for &ndash; the document. Taking the entire bag, he left the locker room as stealthfully as he came. A little while later, the figure reappeared and placed the bag back in the locker. After checking to see that everything looked the way it was, he closed the locker. As he stepped out of the locker room, a person was on the way in and asked for a towel. &ldquo;Right away, sir,&rdquo; he answered the <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/patron\" target=\"_blank\">patron</a> politely, displaying an <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/angelic\" target=\"_blank\">angelic</a> smile.</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/topic/161868904856/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p721248/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p721248\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p723294/\">囧研究: 男人不喜欢幽默的女生</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p723363/\">哈佛大学推荐20个快乐的习惯</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p452491/\">老干妈回应国外价格翻倍: 就赚外国人的钱!</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p723340/\">看电影学英文:憨豆先生教你给男神买礼物</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p723355/\">英语5000单词记忆方法与技巧</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p723441/\">不只是Thank You: 道谢的13种方法</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p723414/\">迪士尼敲定冰雪奇缘2: 脑洞大开的续集名</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p103560/\">沪江英语资料下载帮助及沪元知识</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p456838/\">小考拉树上睡觉被洒水器淋醒  可爱囧态萌翻网友</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p544682/\">喝咖啡的最佳时间：上午10点半！</a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http://www.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江网</a>  <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江英语</a>  <a href=\"http://jp.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江日语</a>  <a href=\"http://fr.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江法语</a>  <a href=\"http://kr.hujiang.com\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江韩语</a></div><hr style=\"border: 0.5px solid gray;\" />", 
